description: This week on The Cigar Authority, two Cigar Stars for the price of one! Omar de Frias from Fratello Cigars joins us along side Phil Zanghi from Debonaire Cigars and Rum. As an extra bonus, Mr Jonathan took the day off making this week's Cigar Authority even BETTER!
